Original author "Dasic"

Info;

Version 3 is now out! I made some small performance improvments and added a "mountain" terrain around the map.

The map was originally planned as "clan map" but is now open to the public.

Bots work OK but not "shocking" well since the map was planned for humans from the start.

Please contact me if anything regarding the map.

Enjoy!
